        <mxCell id="legend" value="Legend&#xa;━━━ Public HTTPS ingress: Internet → IGW → cross-AZ ALB → web tier&#xa;━━━ App → database (MySQL); ══ synchronous RDS replication (auto-failover)&#xa;┄┄┄ Egress: web tier → NAT gateway (per AZ); media to/from Amazon S3&#xa;Dashed boxes = AWS subnets, one set per Availability Zone (no single-AZ SPOF)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FAFAFA;strokeColor=#BDBDBD;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
